As Olimpíadas da Economia são o maior projeto de formação económica em Portugal, destinado a alunos do ensino secundário.
Têm como objetivo Unir dos Mundos: unir os jovens portugueses ao gosto pela ciência económica e unir o Ensino Secundário ao Ensino Superior, em especial à Universidade de Coimbra.
A iniciativa foi criada em 2013 por um grupo de alunos da Licenciatura em Economia da FEUC, sendo atualmente organizada por alunos e alumni da Universidade de Coimbra e por participantes das edições anteriores das OE.
As OE VIII são apoiadas por um Conselho Científico e Pedagógico, composto integralmente por docentes da FEUC - Faculdade de Economia da Universidade de Coimbra.
A participação nas OE VIII destina-se aos todos os alunos do ensino secundário e profissional das escolas de Portugal. Na presente edição o tema em debate será “Portugal 2030”.
As OE VIII decorrem em 3 Fases:
• Fase Escolar, a 17 de fevereiro;
• Fase Regional, a 6 de março;
• Fase Nacional, de 14 a 15 de maio;
Com mais de 8000 participações ao longo das edições transatas, as OE continuam a procurar elevar o seu compromisso com o sistema de ensino português e promover a melhoria da literacia económica em Portugal. Sê parte de nós!!

应用介绍：
校体云（青少年体质健康管理系统）——为中小学生提供体质健康的监测、检测、采集、数据分析、数据平台、运动处方、体育课改等一系列学校体育信息化与学生体质健康整体解决方案。

【产品特点】
@提升学生体质健康，专家团队专业分析
@体测体质 语系转换丨发现孩子体质弱项，针对性改善
@定制化 改善方案丨让每个学生都有自己的运动“私教”
@个性化 健康食谱丨绘制孩子专属生长曲线，专业有营养
@AI科技 体感运动丨 精准动作识别 实时智能纠错

一句话简介：校体云----青少年体质健康管理系统

Educational games for children which will help your baby spend his time with an electronic device effectively. You will visit Bimi Boo’s friends who live on a wondrous island. You will play developing games with a kittens, funny birds and cute squirrel.

The application includes simple games intended to develop fine motor skills and that will entertain your child with bright colors, nice characters and interesting tasks:

- Arrange object by color, form, number and size;
- Use logic when selecting series of items;
- Put geometrical figures on the silhouette;
- Sort things in the right order;
- Restore pictures from memory.

Designed for children of preschool age and also suitable for boys and girls 2- 5 years old. All the activities were developed with participation of experts in the field of children education and include such educational elements as puzzles, sorting and logical games.

The application contains the following developing and educative games for children:

- Items sorting – you need to put food into the fridge and clothes into the wardrobe;
- Logic tasks in the game with a train – help cute kittens get home and deliver food for them;
- Thinking activities where your kid will arrange items in the baskets;
- Logical thinking tasks where your child will sort things by their features.

1. Knowledge in Life：
- Ten daily life topics include: Transportation, Animals, Nature, Community, Health and Hygiene, School, Go Green, Food, Self and Family, People who help us;
- Children have access to diverse topics according to their interests and age;
- Provides activities, worksheets and project exploration.


2. School-Based Curriculum：
- Exclusive for School Users;
- A Multi-media Learning Platform for schools;
- Easy for schools to organise learning topics;
- Allows parents and children to review learning progress in school.


3. Origin of Chinese characters：
- Selects 52 of the most frequently-used characters in kindergarten;
- Introduces strokes, pronunciation and the evolution of characters with fun animations;
- Provides word-matching games.


4. Festival：
- Different animated stories including Christmas, Lunar New Year and Mid-Autumn Festival etc.;
- Allows children to gain better understanding of different festivals.


5. Language (Chinese)：
- Handpicks 90 animated stories about the language according to ten daily life topic for K1-K3 children;
- Introduces new words and sentence structures;
- Enhances children’s language ability.


6. Explore 360:
- New animations updated every week;
- Provides Cantonese, Putonghua and English versions;
- Contents are fun, informative and engaging;
- Includes topics related to children’s daily lives and moral education.


